dct_title_s: Terrae Sanctae tabula è Scripturae Sacrae, Flavii Josephi, Eusebii et Divi Hieronymi ... delineata
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Published after the author's death by his brother Joseph-Nicolas Delisle. Labeled A35 and B35. From: Atlas moderne ... / par plusiers autuers. Paris, 1771-1783.
